# Import pannel settings
You can hand jam it into a tar archive and it's "saved."
Code: Select all
tar cf xfce4panel.tar .config/xfce4/panel
or save the whole desktop setup:

Code: Select all

tar cf xfce4.tar .config

To restore in some other home directory:

Code: Select all

tar xf xfce4panel.tar
